txt.en: Minas Caul is north-west tower of the Witch-king's palace. It is rumoured that the other eight Nazgûl occasionally reside within these towers, wielding dark sorceries at the behest of the Witch-king.

Minas Agar is the western tower of the Witch-king's palace. It is rumoured that the other eight Nazgûl occasionally reside within these towers, wielding dark sorceries at the behest of the Witch-king.

The ancient fortress of the Witch-king of Angmar is rumoured to be surrounded by eight dread towers within which his lieutenants resided during the long war with Arnor, weaving their dread magic there against the forces of the West.
